<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_5bd2b9958059.aspx"><b>周颂·般</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson5bd2b9958059">
於皇时周！陟其高山，嶞山乔岳，允犹翕河。敷天之下，裒时之对。时周之命。
